"Fars dag"                    cultural on second sunday in november
"Nyårsafton"                  cultural on december 31

:: Seasonal And Daylight Savings
"Skottdagen"                  seasonal on ((leapyear year) ? [february 29] : noop)
"Sommartid"                   seasonal on ((year == 1980) ? [first sunday in april] : noop)
"Sommartid"                   seasonal on ((year >= 1981) ? [last sunday in march] : noop)
"Vintertid"                   seasonal on ((year >= 1996) ? [last sunday in october] : ((year >= 1980) ? [last sunday in september] : noop))
"Krav på vinterdäck upphör"   seasonal on april 1
"Krav på vinterdäck"          seasonal on december 1

